# Markdown Example

## Layout

this is __bold__ some text.

## Printing Variables

Variables can be shown using $ {var}, e.g. $ {user} to show the current user: ${user}

## Printing Context Variables

If the ?page=... mechanism is used, we can show the current value: ${value.LAST_NAME}

## Additional Context

Using the context expression, we can define additional context variables. Here, we use the $traverse method to print the boss' last name: ${context.LAST_NAME}
